// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1919 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 600be491-dd60-58b6-a15c-e0af2f171cc6

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
